Package: ppcviz
Title: Diagnostics and Recommendations for Visual Predictive Checks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Package", "Author", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the novel contributions from Sailynoja, Johnson, Martin &
    Vehtari (2025) <arXiv:2503.01509> "Recommendations for visual predictive checks
    in Bayesian workflow". Provides tools to (1) compute visualization PIT values
    that test whether a chosen plot type faithfully represents the data distribution,
    (2) run goodness-of-fit diagnostics for visualizations using simultaneous ECDF
    confidence bands, (3) detect data properties (discreteness, bounds, point masses),
    (4) produce PAVA-based calibration plots for binary and discrete outcomes, and
    (5) automatically recommend appropriate posterior predictive check plots.
